{"tid":1212575,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【粉塵爆炸】15年台灣彩色派對塵爆慘劇 導致15死484傷","createTime":"2019-06-12T19:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:02:53.000Z","uid":216555,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4ed8a4c2f8097b8f84c78b4ed11e21905c976b","tid":1212575,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:39:27.000Z","msg":"主舞台突然起火，加上疑有燃灼性的不明粉末擴散，造成現場逾百民眾灼傷。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學宿舍，有學生在生日會期間撒麵粉，導致發生懷疑塵爆事件，釀成12名男女學生燒傷送院。同類事件，台灣也曾發生，2015年八仙樂園彩色派對粉塵爆炸事件，造成15死484傷慘劇，其中6名傷者是港人﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1FHttzK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1FHttzK&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMW8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=e4373fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1FHttzK</a> ﹞。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【粉塵爆炸】爆炸粉塵逾300種 粉塵粒子越細越易爆　<br />\n<br />\n活動當日有人用疑似加上色素的玉米澱粉導致火災事故，台檢方翻看事故現場錄影片段，起火地點是在舞台右前方開始引燃，並迅速蔓延，舞台西側粉塵疑似遇高熱燈光或吸煙明火引爆。當時現場粉塵濃度極高，舞台及兩側共安裝26支二氧化碳氣瓶炮管，用氣體推進噴灑粉末，人群中還埋伏數名「機槍手」隨機噴射氣體和粉末，群眾進場時也獲派粉塵包。"},{"pid":"5e119d6dcfb5a783eae1ff6271bcb99a5b4643ca","tid":1212575,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:45:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/52KU4LC_dww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F52KU4LC_dww&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMW8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=af744599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/52KU4LC_dww</a><br />\n好危險⚠️"},{"pid":"43b44d92b47c20e838799dfd41ac42178d205a65","tid":1212575,"uid":245379,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一連累埋自己友 你負唔負擔得起"},{"pid":"04647a213ecdc966d5081d2ff0d1ba61cf1268ee","tid":1212575,"uid":216555,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"43b44d92b47c20e838799dfd41ac42178d205a65","tid":1212575,"uid":245379,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:57:35.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/